Package org.knime.base.node.viz.histogram.node Description

Contains classes for KNIME nodes which uses the classes of the histogram package to display a histogram view. The HistogramNode node allows the user to change the columns for the x coordinate and aggregation column in the view by contrast the FixedColumnHistogramNode node allows the selection of these columns only in the node dialog and doesn't supports hiliting in order to allow the browsing of huge data sets.
